items.title: Q2 results this week: Swiggy, Adani Green, ITC, L&T among 300-plus firms set to declare September earnings, Maruti Q2
items.description: Over 300 companies, including major names like Adani, ITC, Larsen & Toubro, and Swiggy, are set to announce Q2 FY26 results this week. Earnings from sectors spanning energy, banking, consumer goods, and manufacturing will provide insights into corporate performance amid volatile commodity prices, shifting consumer demand, and changing monetary conditions. Investors will watch for trends in profitability and market sentiment.
